{
  "stem": "21089.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they think is that I am Volksdeutsche because I told them that my mother was German, which is true.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they would say in cases like that, was [INAUDIBLE] Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I said, no, I am a Pole, because I was Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I knew German, because I told him I had in the school, and I had in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't hide what it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so they accepted that I-- why I am speaking so well German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they knew where I come from, and what my father did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they call me always-- and they was telling me things which I didn't ask.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we knew where they expecting the convoys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But our underground has also-- they knew also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So slow down the convoys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When we slow down the convoys, the convoys which have been going on to Eastern Front, from west to east, supply or other things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 19-- started in 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was after '44, all the activities, to June, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we had-- we received nails to spread the nails on the road, but not-- so they-- they had to stop, and change the tires, and went on the way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we slow down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But later, didn't work, because they had the spares.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had been told to do it in many places, so they would run out of the spares, and had to stop and repair the tires.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but this still wasn't so efficient.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, but what they did-- later, they came with the magnets on front of the convoys with magnets and brushes, big wire brushes, like a cleaning of the street with the-- with the such instrument.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
